{"TopicId":133445,"ForumId":44,"TopicTitle":"ESA planning to build an international vilage...on the moon (article link)","CreatedByName":"Vist","CreatedById":146781,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-03T23:26:44Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Vist","CreatedById":146781,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-03T23:26:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust saw this on the net:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://www.universetoday.com/127648/esa-planning-to-build-an-international-village-on-the-moon/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EESA PLANNING TO BUILD AN INTERNATIONAL VILLAGE\u2026 ON THE MOON!\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spaceception","CreatedById":152800,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-03T23:34:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222440566\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022133445\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221457047604\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022146781\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vist\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 minutes ago, Vist said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust saw this on the net:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://www.universetoday.com/127648/esa-planning-to-build-an-international-village-on-the-moon/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EESA PLANNING TO BUILD AN INTERNATIONAL VILLAGE\u2026 ON THE MOON!\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027d help if you searched for similar threads first \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/130010-lunar-dreams-episode-7-esa-the-moon-awakens-cancelled/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0026amp;embedComment=2364291\u0026amp;embedDo=findComment#comment-2364291\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"fredinno","CreatedById":143381,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-03T23:52:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222440566\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022133445\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221457047604\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022146781\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vist\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n24 minutes ago, Vist said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust saw this on the net:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://www.universetoday.com/127648/esa-planning-to-build-an-international-village-on-the-moon/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EESA PLANNING TO BUILD AN INTERNATIONAL VILLAGE\u2026 ON THE MOON!\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s not serious, it has too little support from member nations to succeed right now. First, we need an ATV-derived manned capsule. THEN, we\u0027ll talk about the moon as a possibility.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bill Phil","CreatedById":127797,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-03T23:53:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222440612\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022133445\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221457049140\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022143381\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022fredinno\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, fredinno said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s not serious, it has too little support from member nations to succeed right now. First, we need an ATV-derived manned capsule. THEN, we\u0027ll talk about the moon as a possibility.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOrion uses an ATV derived service module, or it did.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"fredinno","CreatedById":143381,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-04T03:28:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222440613\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022133445\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221457049204\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022127797\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Bill Phil\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, Bill Phil said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOrion uses an ATV derived service module, or it did.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt does, but it\u0027s not operated by Europe.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Scotius","CreatedById":57622,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-04T20:31:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah. ESA should start their own manned space program, before starting talks about Moon base. Right now it looks like a cross of wishful thinking and PR stunt.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbart","CreatedById":78303,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-04T20:43:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nQuote\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:\u0027PT Sans\u0027, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:26px;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;float:none;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003EIn fact, the company\u003C/span\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://www.sciencealert.com/mit-scientists-have-charted-the-optimal-route-to-mars\u0022 style=\u0022color:rgb(83,110,123);text-decoration:none;text-transform:none;font-family:\u0027PT Sans\u0027, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:26px;text-indent:0px;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;background:rgb(255,255,255);\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Eestimated\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:\u0027PT Sans\u0027, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:26px;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;float:none;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003Ethat if such a base included refueling stations, it could cut the cost of any future Mars missions by about $10 billion a year.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI say, why stop there? If you\u0027re going to pull numbers out of where-the-sun-don\u0027t-shine, why not claim saving as $500 billion a year. Or One Billion Billion?\u00A0\u003Cem\u003EThe program will pay for itself!\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/2SnGpy0.jpg\u0022 alt=\u00222SnGpy0.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spaceception","CreatedById":152800,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-06T12:44:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222441968\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022133445\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221457124182\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002278303\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kerbart\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 3/4/2016 at 0:43 PM, Kerbart said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00222SnGpy0.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/2SnGpy0.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nScott Manley?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"lugge","CreatedById":143343,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-06T13:37:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat the f... did they smoke?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDidn\u0027t they learn from the we\u0027re-about-to-conquer-solar-system-70th-hype??\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell, I\u0027m glad \u0022my\u0022 space agency has ambitious goals. But, well, they overshot...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vist","CreatedById":146781,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-07T07:26:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222440579\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022133445\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00